metadata.description:
Geoffrey Woo's Genesis Collection: January 2022

Geoffrey Woo is an inventor, scientist, and artist. He holds five US Patents and is co-author of two peer-reviewed science papers. He is co-founder of Archive (archive.com), Health Via Modern Nutrition (hvmn.com), and Anti Fund Investment Fund (antifund.vc). He earned a BS with Honors and Distinction in Computer Science from Stanford University.
